      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", or lightsomeness and cheerfulness of spirit, as explained by the two next words: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and gladness and joy; at the good news of their deliverance, so unexpected by them; thus light is explained by gladness, Psalm 97:11 ",
        "children": [
